field.title: scale_ago
field.formula:
CASE [scale]
    WHEN 'День'     THEN AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'day', 1)
    WHEN 'Неделя'    THEN AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'week', 1)
    WHEN 'Месяц'   THEN AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'month', 1)
    WHEN 'Квартал' THEN AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'quarter', 1)
    WHEN 'Год'    THEN AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'year', 1)
    ELSE AGO(COUNTD([flight_id]), [date_by_scale], 'month', 1)
END
